Marker candidates (v1)

Source: R/data.R
marker_candidates_v1.Rd

Data from The Genome Aggregation Database (gnomAD) for binary SNP loci with rs names, i.e., where the rs column starts with rs, there is one character in the ref column and one character in the alt column.

Usage

marker_candidates_v1

Format

An object of class tbl_df (inherits from tbl, data.frame) with 4128 rows and 23 columns.

Source

https://gnomad.broadinstitute.org/

Details

The loci are filtered by MAF values for AFR, EAS, and NFE populations. The MAF values must be within 0.1, 0.15, 0.2 from 0.5.
